Pantheon Markets + Grand Bazaar

1. The Core Structure

Think of the ecosystem as layers of trade:

Campfires → Local Markets → Grand Bazaar → Canon / Library

	•	Campfires = conversation and idea formation
	•	Local markets = specialized exchanges
	•	Grand Bazaar = discovery and cross-domain trade
	•	Canon / Library = stabilized artifacts

Campfires produce ideas.
Markets refine them.
The bazaar connects them.

